# Unsplash API Configuration
# Get your access key from: https://unsplash.com/developers
# 
# 1. Sign up at https://unsplash.com/developers
# 2. Create a new application
# 3. Copy your Access Key
# 4. Add it to your .env file (this file is gitignored)
#
# Free tier: 50 requests/hour (demo mode)
# For production, you can apply for higher rate limits

UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=your_unsplash_access_key_here
